    <div class="comment searchable">
      <p>
I want to bump this, because I just spent 30 minutes trying to figure out why I wasn't seeing the behavior I expected from the documentation.  (My expectation was exactly the behavior proposed here -- if <em>obj</em> is a model, return the permissions based on the content type.)<br />
</p>
<p>
If nothing else, the documentation should note that what it's describing is <strong>inapplicable under the default configuration</strong>.<br />
</p>

